      <title>高盛子公司以 20 亿欧元从 BC Partners 收购制药商 Synthon</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/goldman-unit-buys-2-billion-drugmaker-synthon-from-bc-partners</link>
