    <item>
      <title>欧盟今年最后一次碳排放拍卖是 2020 年以来最便宜的一次</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/last-eu-carbon-auction-of-the-year-is-the-cheapest-since-2020</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟 2024 年碳排放配额的最终拍卖于周一以每公吨 63.64 欧元的价格结算，这是自 2020 年以来最便宜的年底拍卖，当时的碳排放许可价格还不到今天价格的一半。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/last-eu-carbon-auction-of-the-year-is-the-cheapest-since-2020</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 17:16:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Bnef：欧洲能源转型进展顺利吗？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-16/bnef-is-europe-s-energy-transition-on-track</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲能源转型的关键十年即将过去，2030 年气候目标也即将实现。但该地区能否在未来五年内实现目标？彭博新能源财经欧洲能源转型团队分析师索菲亚·佩雷利-罗科 (Sofia Perelli-Rocco) 为您带来更多内容。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-16/bnef-is-europe-s-energy-transition-on-track</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 17:15:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>收购皇家邮政的捷克交易员丹尼尔·克雷廷斯基 (Daniel Kretinsky) 是谁？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/who-is-daniel-kretinsky-why-is-czech-dealmaker-buying-royal-mail</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹尼尔·克雷廷斯基 (Daniel Kretinsky) 花了十多年的时间在欧洲各地建立业务网络，从发电站到零售连锁店和媒体网点，最近专注于财务困难资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/who-is-daniel-kretinsky-why-is-czech-dealmaker-buying-royal-mail</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 17:01:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>施纳贝尔称欧洲央行可以继续降息但降速不会太快</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/ecb-can-keep-cutting-rates-but-not-too-quickly-schnabel-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行执委会成员伊莎贝尔·施纳贝尔表示，随着通胀降至 2% 目标的信心上升，欧洲央行可以继续降低借贷成本，但不应加快进一步举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/ecb-can-keep-cutting-rates-but-not-too-quickly-schnabel-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 16:52:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴里克可能因与政府的争端而关闭马里矿场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/barrick-may-close-mali-gold-mine-over-dispute-with-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴里克黄金公司表示，马里军政府已经阻止了该国最大金矿的货运，如果货运继续暂停，该公司将需要停止该矿的作业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/barrick-may-close-mali-gold-mine-over-dispute-with-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 12:56:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
